OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRussia passes 'Answer to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBlinken' gay propaganda law
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Russia's lower house of parliament has 
OL,6, unanimously voted to extend its ban on 
OL,7, so-called "gay propaganda".            
OL,9,FUnder the latest version of the law,   
OL,10,Fany promotion of homosexuality -       
OL,11,Fincluding in books, films and online - 
OL,12,Fis illegal and carries heavy penalties.
OL,14,FIt was nicknamed the "Answer to        
OL,15,FBlinken" law, after the US Secretary of
OL,16,FState Antony Blinken criticised it as a
OL,17,F"blow to freedom of expression".       
OL,19,FActivists say it is a further attempt  
OL,20,Fto repress Russia's LGBT community.    
